These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
Birthday: may, september, july, june
1. Birthday:september is between Birthday:july and Birthday:june##2
2. Birthday:september is on the left of Birthday:july##1
3. Birthday:may is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Birthday   | may | june | september | july |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
Movie-Genre: fantasy, epic, satire, mystery
1. Movie-Genre:mystery is on the right of Movie-Genre:epic##1
2. Movie-Genre:satire is on the right of Movie-Genre:fantasy##1
3. Movie-Genre:mystery is between Movie-Genre:epic and Movie-Genre:fantasy##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | mystery | fantasy | satire |

 #################################
 
